    "Ask the student to pick an organizational issue or problem they would like to explore.",
    "1.Make sure the case has all the details a student would need to consider the problem or make a recommendation.",
    "Make whatever assumptions you need to make to create the case.",
    "2.If the case includes data, ask the student for the data or ask if you should create a data set to suit the case.",
